text: Neophrissoma rotundipenne is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1938.BioLib.cz - Neophrissoma rotundipenne. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1938
